{"tid":1077910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高雄農業僅占總產值0.2％  從業人口不到5%      他分析韓國瑜狂推銷背後原因...","createTime":"2019-03-26T02:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T05:06:12.000Z","uid":35790,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ab4dc1435cc7b84c3da759f85c10eace03cfc6e2","tid":1077910,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:14:32.000Z","msg":"高雄農業僅占總產值0.2％ 他分析韓國瑜狂推銷背後原因...<br />\n<br />\n2019-03-26<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕高雄市長韓國瑜上任以來主打農業，但臉書粉專「蕪菁雜誌」指出，其實農業產值占高雄總產值僅0.2%，從業人口不到5%，反而是製造業占產值一半以上，「蕪菁雜誌」分析，韓國瑜把版面放在農業有其考量。<br />\n<br />\n「蕪菁雜誌」指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">第一「農業非常容易被中共操控」，馬英九時代以來，台灣農業外銷依賴中國單一市場</span>，像是金鑽鳳梨有97%是運往中國，價格任中國宰割。<span style=\"color: red;\">第二「台灣農民賭性堅強，產銷亂無章法，賺錢自己賺，賠錢賴政府」</span>，每年出現農民搶種某一作物，結果供過於求，卻要政府買單，容易遭到小道消息操控，責怪執政者。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第三「農業產值小，『政治訂單』成本低，配合媒體宣傳，c/p值超高」，農業占高雄總產值僅0.2%，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中國只要丟一點錢都能造成軒然大波</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n「蕪菁雜誌」強調，並非市府不用照顧農民，事實上陳菊也做了很多，像是打下星馬通路，但韓國瑜拼農業的路線完全錯誤，拿的MOU都是政治採購，「哪天高雄的利用價值沒有了，一翻臉這些MOU都成了歷史文件」。<br />\n<br />\n「蕪菁雜誌」感嘆，韓國瑜拼的是自己的速食知名度，還有開木馬後門給中國，而非高雄經濟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2738816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2738816&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=0d3fadcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2738816&h=b2e2370b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2738816</a>"},{"pid":"85d57c65f9c2aa123217478ee7f3b7a67fa32bb7","tid":1077910,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:15:22.000Z","msg":"賣台之旅"},{"pid":"ef719cf51ee08730508f86c45480cac778dee9b3","tid":1077910,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24688253ff237b4eda5632a36b36634bdbc8d1d3","tid":1077910,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:59:08.000Z","msg":"台灣人係人係豬，睇下屆總統選舉就知"},{"pid":"e712fb5d6fd91cefff66cf4af9d926526e92c293","tid":1077910,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T03:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4482e99c03f2a599638263f155cd80fe05bda590","tid":1077910,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}